Imo Governor Hope Uzodinma has appointed celebrity barman, Cubana Chief Priest as a Special Adviser. Cubana Chief Priest, who used to work with Obi Cuban before going solo, was appointed the Governor’s Special Adviser on social media influence and social events management. The celebrity barman took to his Instagram page to share the news.   Ex- BBNaija’s Nini Singh shows off six cars worth N55m     Kemi Akindoju: I cry to appreciate art, song or film     King Sunny Ade, NCC DG reward blind singer, Chude Mountain   He posted: ” I have an instruction from his excellency to make over 1000 Imo State youths super successful like me from the almighty social media which made me in just one year, it’s so easy for me to do and I will do just that through Christ who strengthens me, Amen. - Advertisement - “May God give me grace, wisdom, energy and guts to tell his excellency the unfiltered truth he needs to hear at all times.”